---
import '../styles/global.css';
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <meta name="robots" content="noindex" />
    <title>Welcome — Replicata</title>
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' viewBox='0 0 100 100'%3E%3Ctext y='.9em' font-size='90'%3E%E2%9A%99%EF%B8%8F%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E" />
  </head>
  <body class="bg-zinc-950 text-zinc-200 font-sans antialiased">
    <header class="border-b border-zinc-900">
      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-4 flex items-center justify-between">
        <a href="/" class="text-xl font-semibold text-white">replicata</a>
      </div>
    </header>

    <section class="max-w-lg mx-auto px-6 py-24 text-center">
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white">You're in.</h1>
      <p class="mt-4 text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed">
        Your license key is on its way to your email. It starts with <code class="text-emerald-300">REP_-</code>.
      </p>

      <div class="mt-10 text-left rounded-xl border border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-900/50 p-6 space-y-4">
        <h2 class="text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-300 uppercase tracking-wider">Next steps</h2>
        <ol class="space-y-3 text-sm text-zinc-400 list-decimal list-inside">
          <li>Check your email for the license key</li>
          <li>Open Replicata — <code class="text-emerald-300">./replicata</code></li>
          <li>Paste the key in the activation screen</li>
          <li>Done — start connecting apps</li>
        </ol>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-8 text-sm text-zinc-500 space-y-2">
        <p>Don't have Replicata yet? <a href="/download" class="text-emerald-400 hover:text-emerald-300 underline">Download it here</a>.</p>
        <p>Key not arriving? Check spam, or email <a href="mailto:hello@replicata.dev" class="text-emerald-400 hover:text-emerald-300 underline">hello@replicata.dev</a>.</p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </body>
</html>
